metadata.description: This access pass includes: One (1) Entry to the Summit. One (1) Commemorative Artwork NFT by XCopy, Moxarra and Neurocolor. One (1) Free Access Pass to (1) VOYU Experience in Mexico City during the week of Nov 7-11th.
